There are many AI image generators available, such as DALL-E 2, Midjourney, and Stable Diffusion. **To help you choose the right tool, we've put together a detailed [comparison of AI image generators](best-ai-writing-tools-comparison.md).**

### Enter a prompt

Enter a prompt that describes the image you want to generate. Be as specific as possible.

### Generate images

The AI image generator will generate a set of images based on your prompt.

### Select an image

Select the image that you want to use for your blog post.

